title: 104: 2016 NFL Draft Recap
itunes:title: 104: 2016 NFL Draft Recap
description:
Former NFL Scouts Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks breakdown the2016 NFL Draft, including the picks they liked and didn't like fromeach round. Then, to wrap the podcast they share each team's bestvalue pick from this years draft.
